  <text x="20" y="30" fill="#fafafa" font-size="16" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Bitcoin Knots' Node-Share Surge vs. Core-Knots OP_RETURN Policy Gap</text>
  <g font-family="sans-serif">
    <text x="20" y="60" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13">1. Knots node share over time (% of all reachable nodes)</text>
    <rect x="20" y="75" width="660" height="36" rx="8" fill="#3f3f46"/>
    <text x="350" y="99" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="13" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle">First half of 2025: 12% to 19%</text>
